      </relatedmaterial>
      <arrangement id="aspace_79499982f9fcc7a9346c48003532ea99">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The material in the original accession is arranged chronologically. Additions to the collection may vary in arrangement.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_5aa1f293ec99af99e9e73b05e0429b2b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of printed material relating to the political and social conditions in Eritrea and a photograph album of life in Eritrea.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
